Definition.WordDefinition:
HMO \HMO\ n. [acronym for Health Maintenance Organization.] A health maintenance organization; a form of group health insurance that entitles members to services of participating hospitals and clinics and physicians. [acronym]
Syn: health maintenance organization. [WordNet 1.5]
HMO n : group insurance that entitles members to services of participating hospitals and clinics and physicians [syn: {health maintenance organization}]
